Flame Graph demos from the talk "Blazing Performance with Flame Graphs"
(USENIX/LISA 2013), plus MySQL EXPLAIN demos for this project.

MySQL EXPLAIN demos (mysql-query-*.svg):
  Flame graph, bar chart, and treemap examples from EXPLAIN ANALYZE JSON.
  See the main README for how to generate them.

These SVGs cannot be viewed on GitHub directly; clone or download the repo,
then open them in a browser (file://...) or use the docs index on GitHub Pages.
